    "title": "Senior Doctor - RML Hospital Holdings Services - Growth Opportunity",
    "description": "We at RML Hospital Holdings Services are looking for an experienced Senior Doctor based out of Ahmedabad. If you are a result-oriented professional with a passion for excellence, we want to hear from you.\n\nAbout RML Hospital Holdings Services:\nRML Hospital Holdings Services is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Provide high-quality patient care and maintain patient records\n• Respond to medical emergencies and provide immediate care\n• Coordinate with multidisciplinary teams for comprehensive patient management\n• Maintain sterile environments and follow infection control protocols\n• Diagnose and treat medical conditions following established protocols\n• Conduct routine health assessments and screenings\n• Educate patients and families on health management and disease prevention\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Arch / M.Arch from recognized institution\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Patient Care\n• Proficiency in CPT Codes\n• Proficiency in Health Informatics\n• Proficiency in EMR/EHR\n• Proficiency in BLS/ACLS\n• Proficiency in HIPAA Compliance\n• Proficiency in Medical Terminology\n• Proficiency in Pharmacovigilance\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Flexible working hours\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Ahmedabad, Gujarat, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with RML Hospital Holdings Services!",
